seal     : A non-magical girl sees a dazzling witch's show as a child and decides, against all odds, to become a witch herself. At Luna Nova, an academy where magic is fading and the rules say talent is inherited, Akko has nothing but stubborn wonder — and a legendary wand that answers only to belief. A bright, hand-drawn hymn to enthusiasm in a world that has lost it.
